layout: default.njk
title: Archives
---

{% set archives = collections.articles | archives %}
{# meta data paragraph #}
{% set avg =  ((collections.articles | length) / archives.yearStats.spread) | round(2) %}
<p>Over the last {{ archives.yearStats.spread }} years Iâ€™ve written {{ collections.articles | length }} articles. I write an average of {{ avg }} articles per year. My most prolific year was {{ archives.yearStats.busiest.year }} when I wrote {{ archives.yearStats.busiest.count }} {{ 'article' | plural(archives.yearStats.busiest.count) }}. By contrast, the quietest year was {{ archives.yearStats.quietest.year }} with {{ archives.yearStats.quietest.count }} {{ 'article' | plural(archives.yearStats.quietest.count) }}.</p>

{# render posts #}
{%- for year in archives.years -%}
  <h2>{{ year }}</h2>
    <dl class="summary-list">
    {%- for article in archives.posts[year] -%}
      <div class="summary-list-row">
        <dt><a href="{{ article.url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></dt>
        <dd><time class="teaser-date" datetime="{{ article.date | date('') }}">{{ article.date | date }}</time><dd>
      </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
    </dl>
{%- endfor -%}